&lt;li&gt;Design AI-centered user experiences that leverage recommendation systems, intelligent automation,&lt;br&gt;conversational interfaces, predictive intelligence, decision-support workflows, and agentic interaction&lt;br&gt;models.&lt;/li&gt;
